Name: Stinky Snake
About the game: After being shipwrecked on a tropical island, Snake, Puppy, and Angel are ambushed by a Skunk who kidnaps Puppy and Angel. Snake must explore the island and rescue his family from Skunk. Using the set of tools he will collect along the way, he fights the army of skunks that stand between him and his family. Then once he has found his family, Snake must break the curse of the cart he used to complete his quest in order to leave the island.
